Yeah. This is my first 'serious' map. It isn't that much for you maybe, but it was good for me to learn some of Hammer's stuff. I made this map, using standard Valve tex's, no 3d skybox is in this either. Much thanks to Arvis for helping me.

It's V2 just because i extended the small map i made from the beginning. It's bigger and you can't see eachothers spawn bunkers from the beginning.
